content: StPaulTim renamed stream General to Backdrop.
Thanks for doing this @StPaulTim :+1: ...so far it does make sense.

After much discussion in Zulip today and some additional discussion during dev meeting, we decided to deprecate the contrib and code review streams. For now, I simply made the contrib stream read only, so you can still access existing messages. I think that eventually, we will delete it but that decision is for another day.
